    </p>
    <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--ink-soft);">
      <!-- TODO(amy): confirm the contact email address, or swap in a form
           service (Formspree/Tally) if you prefer submissions over email. -->
      For consulting and implementation work, see
